   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.040", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sehr geehrte Damen und Herren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.200", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "24.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "was Sie als GroKo gegen das Auseinanderdriften von Arm und Reich, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "24.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "26.600", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "von Bildungsgewinnern und Abgeh\u00e4ngten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "26.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "29.760", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "gegen Klimakrise und Artensterben tun, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "29.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.040", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das kann ich meinen Patenkindern nicht erkl\u00e4ren."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "34.440", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Gr\u00fcner Anspruch ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "34.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "37.640", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Zukunft unserer Wissensnation zu gestalten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "37.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "43.840", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihr Koalitionsvertrag ist zukunftsvergessen und nicht enkeltauglich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "43.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.800", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Bildung und Forschung sind Quelle k\u00fcnftigen Wohlstandes, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "52.040", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00f6nnen Chancengerechtigkeit erm\u00f6glichen und sind Voraussetzung f\u00fcr eine innovative, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "52.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "55.160", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "kreative und auch weltoffene Gesellschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "55.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.120", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Koalitionsvertrag entwickelt hierzu keinen Spirit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.760", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Ihre Vereinbarungen bleiben St\u00fcckwerk."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "62.800", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Was Deutschland stattdessen braucht, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "62.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "68.840", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ist eine beherzte Strategie zur Bildungsrepublik und zum Innovationsspitzenreiterland."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "68.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.680", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Union regiert seit zw\u00f6lf Jahren"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.840", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und hat seitdem den digitalen Wandel verpennt."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "77.760", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Viele Schulen verharren im Kreidezeitalter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "77.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "79.160", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es fehlt an schnellem Internet, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "79.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.320", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an digitalen Lehrmaterialien, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "85.400", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "an geschulten Lehrkr\u00e4ften und an Medienkompetenzf\u00f6rderung f\u00fcr Kids. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "85.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.640", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Schon vor zwei Jahren haben Sie den DigitalPakt Schule angek\u00fcndigt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "92.920", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber elementare Fragen bleiben weiter ungel\u00f6st: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "92.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "97.040", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie passt ein F\u00fcnfjahrespakt zur Daueraufgabe Digitalisierung? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "97.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "100.000", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie geht es mit Datenschutz und Datensicherheit voran? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "100.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.320", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wer \u00fcbernimmt Wartung und Ersatz der Ger\u00e4te?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "108.760", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Keinesfalls d\u00fcrfen die Kommunen damit alleingelassen werden oder d\u00fcrfen ihnen gar die Kosten aufgeb\u00fcrdet werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "108.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "114.640", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der digitale Wandel unserer Bildungseinrichtungen l\u00e4sst sich jedenfalls mit befristeten Finanzmitteln oder Flugtaxen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "114.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "116.000", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Frau B\u00e4r sie plant, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "116.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.840", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nicht nachhaltig gestalten."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "122.720", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im Koalitionsvertrag fehlt uns ein Masterplan f\u00fcr Bildungsgerechtigkeit."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "122.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "128.840", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der enge Zusammenhang von Chancen und sozialer Herkunft ist die Achillesferse unseres deutschen Bildungssystems. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "128.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "132.320", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum fehlt in Ihrem Koalitionsvertrag das Thema Schulsozialarbeit? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "132.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "137.280", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Warum fehlt ein ambitionierter Plan zur St\u00e4rkung benachteiligter Schulen in armen Quartieren? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "137.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "145.520", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wo bleibt eine Offensive f\u00fcr Integration durch Bildung f\u00fcr Zugewanderte und Gefl\u00fcchtete und f\u00fcr Inklusion als Menschenrecht?"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "145.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.560", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch Ihr angek\u00fcndigter Rechtsanspruch auf Ganztagsbetreuung im Grundschulalter schafft mehr Fragen als Klarheit; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "153.800", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn Betreuung ist nicht gleich Bildung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "153.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "159.600", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ganzt\u00e4giges Lernen und die Vereinbarkeit von Familie und Beruf enden eben nicht nach der vierten Klasse."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "159.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "164.160", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wenn Sie den Rechtsanspruch einfach ins Sozialgesetzbuch\u00a0VIII schreiben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "164.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "170.560", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dann d\u00fcrfen Sie die Familien und auch die Kommunen mit den Kosten und der Umsetzung nicht alleinlassen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "170.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.240", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das w\u00e4re das Mindeste."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "172.800", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "172.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.960", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es braucht bundesweit und dauerhaft gute Ganztagsschulen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "181.440", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Abgeh\u00e4ngte d\u00fcrfen wir uns nicht erlauben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "181.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "188.560", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Chancen f\u00fcr alle und jedes Talent optimal f\u00f6rdern m\u00fcssten Ihr zentrales Ziel sein."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "188.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "189.080", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Chancen- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "189.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "193.440", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Talentf\u00f6rderung par excellence k\u00f6nnte eigentlich das BAf\u00f6G leisten. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "193.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "195.080", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Umso \u00e4rgerlicher ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "195.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.920", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass die GroKo das BAf\u00f6G weiter in die Bedeutungslosigkeit herunterwirtschaften will."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "204.520", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie wollen zuwarten und erst 2021 etwas tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "204.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "205.280", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir sagen: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "205.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.440", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das BAf\u00f6G muss sofort und zackig verbessert werden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.080", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie m\u00fcssen hier klotzen statt kleckern und das BAf\u00f6G regelm\u00e4\u00dfig erh\u00f6hen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "216.200", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Genauso wichtig ist, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "216.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.240", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "endlich etwas gegen die Wohnungsnot in Hochschulst\u00e4dten zu tun. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "224.640", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Studieren und Ausbildung m\u00fcssen besser finanziert werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "224.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "229.960", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und bezahlbares Wohnen f\u00fcr Studis und Azubis ist unerl\u00e4sslich."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "229.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "236.000", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Angehen m\u00fcssen wir die Ausbildungslosigkeit viel zu vieler Jugendlicher. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "236.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "238.600", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Nur noch 20\u00a0Prozent der Betriebe bilden aus. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "238.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "244.240", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mehr als 1,2\u00a0Millionen Menschen zwischen 20 und 29\u00a0Jahren sind ohne Berufsabschluss. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "244.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "245.640", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das sind Probleme, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "245.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.120", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bund und L\u00e4nder gemeinsam mit den Gewerkschaften und Arbeitgebern l\u00f6sen m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "256.120", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ihre geplante Enquete-Kommission zur St\u00e4rkung der beruflichen Bildung und Sicherung des Fachkr\u00e4ftebedarfs mag eine Idee sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "256.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "259.320", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es darf aber keinesfalls das Risiko wachsen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "259.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "261.520", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass weitere Jahre ins Land gehen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "261.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "266.840", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "ohne dass die l\u00e4ngst bekannten Strukturprobleme der beruflichen Bildung angegangen werden, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "266.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "270.880", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil wir noch auf die Ergebnisse der Enquete-Kommission warten m\u00fcssen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "270.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "277.640", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00f6tig ist zackig eine Ausbildungsgarantie f\u00fcr alle Jugendlichen unabh\u00e4ngig von ihrer sozialen und ethnischen Herkunft."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "277.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "285.760", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00f6tig sind gute Ausbildungsverg\u00fctungen und im sp\u00e4teren Arbeitsleben gute L\u00f6hne und Weiterbildungsfinanzierung;"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "285.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "294.760", 
   "id": "s000076", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "denn \u00fcber 5\u00a0Millionen Menschen mit abgeschlossener Berufsausbildung verdienen weniger als 10\u00a0Euro pro Stunde. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "294.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "296.200", 
   "id": "s000077", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Da ist es doch kein Wunder, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "296.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "300.600", 
   "id": "s000078", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass akademische Abschl\u00fcsse attraktiver erscheinen als berufliche. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "300.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "304.520", 
   "id": "s000079", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb fordern wir eine Offensive gegen den Fachkr\u00e4ftemangel. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "304.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "307.560", 
   "id": "s000080", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Junge Menschen brauchen mehr Ausbildungs- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "307.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "309.040", 
   "id": "s000081", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und mehr Studienpl\u00e4tze, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "309.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "315.480", 
   "id": "s000082", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Deutschland braucht mehr Meister und mehr Master."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "315.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "323.400", 
   "id": "s000083", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Im letzten Jahrzehnt hat der Bund mit den L\u00e4ndern \u00fcber die Wissenschaftspakte viele Milliarden an die Hochschulen und die au\u00dferuniversit\u00e4ren Forschungseinrichtungen gegeben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "323.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "325.280", 
   "id": "s000084", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
